      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. that's a good start. but my prof is gonna ask about the counter-arguments, like people who say that redistributing wealth goes against meritocracy and that people should just work for what they earn. how should i address that in my essay so it doesn't make my main argument look weak?",
